0":null,"customfield_11802":null,"customfield_11805":null,"duedate":null,"progress":{"progress":0,"total":480,"percent":0},"customfield_11806":null,"comment":{"comments":[{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/41109/comment/114400","id":"114400","author":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=ethomas","name":"ethomas","key":"ethomas","accountId":"557058:8f092f9a-0724-44c0-84a3-0220705f856a","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/a01d066493c57e5dee4b94dc87395576?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FavatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/a01d066493c57e5dee4b94dc87395576?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26avatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/a01d066493c57e5dee4b94dc87395576?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26avatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/a01d066493c57e5dee4b94dc87395576?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26avatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Evan Thomas","active":false,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"body":"Manual test case:\r\n1) Create the stack shown here\r\n{code}\r\n{\r\n  \"Resources\" : {\r\n    \"SG1\" : {\r\n      \"Type\" : \"AWS::EC2::SecurityGroup\",\r\n      \"Properties\" : {\"GroupDescription\" : \"SG1\"}\r\n    },\r\n    \"SG2\" : {\r\n      \"Type\" : \"AWS::EC2::SecurityGroup\",\r\n      \"Properties\" : {\"GroupDescription\" : \"SG2\"},\r\n      \"DependsOn\" : \"SG1\"\r\n    },\r\n    \"SG3\" : {\r\n      \"Type\" : \"AWS::EC2::SecurityGroup\",\r\n      \"Properties\" : {\"GroupDescription\" : \"SG3\"},\r\n      \"DependsOn\" : \"SG2\"\r\n    },\r\n    \"SG4\" : {\r\n      \"Type\" : \"AWS::EC2::SecurityGroup\",\r\n      \"Properties\" : {\"GroupDescription\" : \"SG4\"},\r\n      \"DependsOn\" : \"SG3\"\r\n    },\r\n    \"SG5\" : {\r\n      \"Type\" : \"AWS::EC2::SecurityGroup\",\r\n      \"Properties\" : {\"GroupDescription\" : \"SG5\"},\r\n      \"DependsOn\" : \"SG4\"\r\n    },\r\n    \"SG6\" : {\r\n      \"Type\" : \"AWS::EC2::SecurityGroup\",\r\n      \"Properties\" : {\"GroupDescription\" : \"SG6\"},\r\n      \"DependsOn\" : \"SG5\"\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n{code}\r\n2) run instances using SG2 and SG4 as security groups\r\n3) try to delete the stack with --retained-resources SG2 (should say can't pass retained resources on a stack not in DELETE_FALED)  (use the aws sdk for now)\r\n4) try to delete stack (no args)\r\n5) try to delete stack (while being deleted) with --retained-resources SG2 (should say delete already in progress)\r\n6) delete should fail (SG2 and SG4 should fail to delete.  It takes more than 5 minutes.)\r\n7) try to delete stack with --retained-resources SG2 should fail but see DELETE_SKIPPED   on SG2  (takes more than 5 minutes)\r\n8) try to delete with --retained-resources SG4 should succeed (quickly)\r\n\r\n","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=ethomas","name":"ethomas","key":"ethomas","accountId":"557058:8f092f9a-0724-44c0-84a3-0220705f856a","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/a01d066493c57e5dee4b94dc87395576?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FavatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/a01d066493c57e5dee4b94dc87395576?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26avatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/a01d066493c57e5dee4b94dc87395576?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26avatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/a01d066493c57e5dee4b94dc87395576?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2